t: "Then when they have ňĻalmostňļ reached the end of their waiting period, either retain them honourably or separate from them honourably.¬†And call two of your reliable men to witness ňĻeither wayňļ‚ÄĒand ňĻlet the witnessesňļ bear true testimony for ňĻthe sake ofňļ Allah. This is enjoined on whoever has faith in Allah and the Last Day. And whoever is mindful of Allah, He will make a way out for them"